are trying to starve him.

49:26.667 --> 49:28.667
- You should have been a cop.

49:30.033 --> 49:31.800
- Did Alvarez tell you this?

49:31.867 --> 49:33.333
How do you know
he's telling the truth?

49:33.400 --> 49:35.133
- Why would he lie?
- Some prisoners,

49:35.200 --> 49:38.100
particularly in Solitary,
become delusional, paranoid.

49:38.166 --> 49:40.100
- How do I find out
if they're feeding him?

49:40.166 --> 49:42.633
If I ask them and it's true,
they're just gonna find

49:42.700 --> 49:43.967
another way to fuck with him.

49:44.033 --> 49:45.467
- Yeah.

49:45.533 --> 49:47.233
- I have to give him
the benefit of the doubt.

49:48.700 --> 49:50.133
- So, what's with the dress?

49:50.200 --> 49:52.233
High holy day or something?

49:56.700 --> 49:58.400
[gate buzzes]

50:03.367 --> 50:05.433
- Miguel.

50:06.734 --> 50:08.767
Give us some privacy.

50:18.400 --> 50:21.333
Here, eat.

50:21.400 --> 50:23.000
- I'm not hungry.

50:23.066 --> 50:24.333
- What do you mean
you're not hungry?

50:24.400 --> 50:26.667
You said you haven't eaten
in two days.

50:26.734 --> 50:28.500
Take the sandwich.

50:28.567 --> 50:29.834
Take the damn sandwich!

50:29.900 --> 50:31.500
- You want the fuckin' sandwich?

50:31.567 --> 50:32.834
Fuck you!

50:32.900 --> 50:34.333
Fucking shit!

50:34.400 --> 50:35.500
Oh, fuck!

50:35.567 --> 50:36.600
- Fucker.

50:36.667 --> 50:38.734
- No. Stop!

50:39.967 --> 50:40.900
- Get the fuck out!

50:40.967 --> 50:42.734
♪ ♪

50:42.800 --> 50:44.233
- Stop it!

50:44.300 --> 50:46.066
Open this door!

50:46.133 --> 50:48.033
For God's sake!

50:50.033 --> 50:52.367
- I think Keller will live.

50:52.433 --> 50:53.967
